'''Pugil''' was a popular sport on the planet [[Lannik/Legends|Lannik]]. Teams included the [[New Osler Flejj Beasts]]. The sport underwent something of a scandal in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]] when [[Rolsat Noviee]], the sport's highest-scoring and highest-paid player, was revealed to be a [[Clawdite/Legends|Clawdite]] changeling disguised as a [[Lannik (species)/Legends|Lannik]].

==Behind the scenes==
*The name "pugil" is likely a reference to "[[Wikipedia:Boxing|pugilism]]," another term for boxing.

